sentences: Early work included recordings of distorted telephone calls and late night television.
In 2007 the Protect & Survive EP was released on the White Label Music record label.
In 2008 Kontour released the album Scanners on Some Bizzare Records, Stevo Pearce is credited as executive producer of the album.
In 2012 Kontour contributed a recording to a project titled A Broadcast to the Trees.
